        favorite = self.favorite
        label = self.label
        parameters: Union[Unset, Dict[str, Any]] = UNSET

            parameters = self.parameters.to_dict()

        field_dict: Dict[str, Any] = {}
        field_dict.update({})

        if parameters is not UNSET:

        return field_dict
